title: NZ universities seeking more opportunities with China (The University of Waikato)
text: ( Source : The University of Waikato ) All eight New Zealand universities are in China this week as part of a Ministerial delegation led by Tertiary Education Minister Steven Joyce . Their goal is to deepen links between the education systems
